{"tid":2508900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民幣18元參加一日遊旅行團 重慶十多名長者被帶去參觀墓地","createTime":"2021-04-29T05:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T08:21:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":208,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cb1e8be20a7da11485371e1d6288af3e978168","tid":2508900,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國重慶日前傳出有10多位長輩，花費人民幣18元（約新台幣77元）參加1日遊旅行團，沒想到竟被帶去墓地，氣得大罵鄭姓召集人，消息曝光後，引發中國網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，這些長輩是經由他人介紹參加低價團，不少人還精心打扮，一路上歡笑不斷，但巴士卻把一行人帶到一處墓地，氣得破口大罵晦氣，鄭姓男子頓時成為眾矢之的。<br />\n<br />\n鄭男無奈表示，事先有詢問每人所需費用、參訪景點，旅遊公司說18元、去景區，「沒有說到陵園」，忍不住直呼「要旅遊就旅遊、要參觀陵園就參觀陵園，不能掛旅遊之名，掛羊頭賣狗肉要不得」。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/novelty/breakingnews/3515373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2Fbreakingnews%2F3515373&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=55add23c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2Fbreakingnews%2F3515373&h=1764d3e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/novelty/breakingnews/3515373</a>"},{"pid":"3fd4f773417f953998b392d950de008522b612ec","tid":2508900,"uid":131696,"like":348,"dislike":1,"score":347,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"帶佢地睇樓有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734a8db34b4da970d40774ae130ba92bb6ef9200","tid":2508900,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c72e5e81118a08f0a8183cef9adf2a27f3d5836","tid":2508900,"uid":155095,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"中國人點解要忌諱死亡<br />\n<br />\n死亡係人生必經嘅階段"},{"pid":"7e2dad2ccc028f45570fa438946371a6be2fafbc","tid":2508900,"uid":28181,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"3fd4f773417f953998b392d950de008