tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國重慶日前傳出有10多位長輩，花費人民幣18元（約新台幣77元）參加1日遊旅行團，沒想到竟被帶去墓地，氣得大罵鄭姓召集人，消息曝光後，引發中國網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，這些長輩是經由他人介紹參加低價團，不少人還精心打扮，一路上歡笑不斷，但巴士卻把一行人帶到一處墓地，氣得破口大罵晦氣，鄭姓男子頓時成為眾矢之的。<br />\n<br />\n鄭男無奈表示，事先有詢問每人所需費用、參訪景點，旅遊公司說18元、去景區，「沒有說到陵園」，忍不住直呼「要旅遊就旅遊、要參觀陵園就參觀陵園，不能掛旅遊之名，掛羊頭賣狗肉要不得」。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/novelty/breakingnews/3515373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2Fbreakingnews%2F3515373&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=55add23c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2Fbreakingnews%2F3515373&h=1764d3e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/novelty/breakingnews/3515373</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"兵馬俑，金字塔咪又係墓地，jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df84e91b01959fbb1d33cfcc64b119cb901850d","tid":2508900,"uid":135866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"阿正同妹頭會唔會去睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d442ac979274c6e95b25cfb8b7f2e21daee2f75e","tid":2508900,"uid":242677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71bb70283359357bf8d8f148ad95ddd8b1233882","tid":2508900,"uid":214502,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"5c72e5e81118a08f0a8183cef9adf2a27f3d5836","tid":2508900,"uid":155095,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"中國人點解要忌諱死亡<br />\n<br />\n死亡係人生必經嘅階段"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:54:29.000Z","msg":"中国人最鐘意逃避問題架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔比講就好似唔會死咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"死亡唔係一個問題<br />\n係中國生活死亡係一種解脫添<br />\n英國既墳場其實好靚"},{"pid":"8b0420d49e6ed719b19edb17529f49a92163de09","tid":2508900,"uid":5490,"like":0,"di